snippet.title: Fragsurf - Combat Surf
snippet.description:
We've spiced up our combat surf gameplay and added a bunch of cool new features. Plus, we're now free to play on Steam.

Fragsurf's Discord: https://discord.gg/fragsurf
Fragsurf on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1033410/Fragsurf/
